sequenceDiagram
    actor Diner
    participant iOS as SwiftUI iOS app
    participant API as Express API
    participant Session as session.js
    participant POS as simulateOrder.js / Toast webhook
    participant WS as Socket.io room
    participant Tab as tabs.json
    participant Checkout as simulateCheckout.js
    participant History as history.json + loyalty.json

    Diner->>iOS: Sign in
    iOS->>API: POST /api/auth/login
    API-->>iOS: Demo user + mock token
    Diner->>iOS: Open Live Tab
    iOS->>Session: POST /api/session/start
    Session->>Tab: Create empty tab
    Session-->>iOS: sessionId
    iOS->>WS: Subscribe to session_<id>
    POS->>API: POST /api/webhook/toast with item states
    API->>Tab: Replace tab items and recalculate totals
    API->>WS: Emit tabUpdated
    WS-->>iOS: tabUpdated event
    iOS->>API: GET /api/tab/:sessionId
    API-->>iOS: Updated items, status, subtotal, tax, total
    Checkout->>Tab: Mark tab paid
    Checkout->>History: Write receipt and loyalty points
